WEBVTT

00:01.968 --> 00:04.436
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:12.679 --> 00:14.947
              Cold outside, huh?

00:15.015 --> 00:17.216
        Yes.                    

00:17.283 --> 00:20.185
              And we got a slush
                    thing going.

00:21.921 --> 00:24.089
So it seems.                    

00:25.558 --> 00:27.226
                    Beer nut?   

00:27.293 --> 00:28.961
No, thank you.                  

00:32.598 --> 00:35.934
              Have you ever been
              with an older man?

00:37.671 --> 00:40.072
Woody, I'm ready                
to settle up.                   

00:40.140 --> 00:42.941
                 I'm not looking
                 for commitment.

00:50.116 --> 00:53.419
Cold outside, huh?              

00:56.356 --> 00:58.290
      (theme song begins)       

