01:08.335 --> 01:11.737
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

01:11.805 --> 01:15.641
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

01:16.743 --> 01:19.211
  ¶ Sometimes you want to go ¶  

